  • Project

    Quake Quiz

    UI Design

    Role

    UI Designer

    Goal

    To design, code, and produce a Flash game, with a primary focus on user interactions.

  • Styles

  • Tools

    • Photoshop CC
    • Flash CC
    • Sketch

  • Details

    A quick Flash demo created in a user interface class. The assignment was to create a youth-friendly quiz to test knowledge of what to do during and after an earthquake. Requirements included having true/false and fill-in-the-blank questions, a self-updating score, and multiple button options.

    The time limit for this assignment was three days. Documentation for this project may be found here.
